{"tid":1426401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！大家盡量利用d區議員或者立法會議員啦","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:29:21.000Z","uid":265339,"like":180,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"0159ef224bb56f707eb319f6b95a9dc6ef5f5ed7","tid":1426401,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:10:51.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得611金鐘個晚d警察又係亂咁查d後生仔，最後d立法會議員到場之後，佢地基本上都收晒皮。<br />\n<br />\n琴日深水埗單野係好嬲，d警察係on9，但好奇怪地連登以前會問有律師或者議員到場未，宜家係會話要人。其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家有出糧</span></span></span>俾班垃圾議員嫁，唔洗咁錫住佢地喎，佢地都無野做嫁啦，叫佢地出黎幫拖啦。雖然宜家議員已經嚇唔到防暴，起碼嚇到散仔啦掛？<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔出就俾d街坊睇清佢地既真面目，出左又可以俾d人知佢地有做野，何樂而不為？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNKdwq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNKdwq9.jpg&h=4ce84838&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DZdwra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DZdwra.png&h=830e6079&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGpAKMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGpAKMd.png&h=4c5578d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAUXX6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAUXX6e.png&h=79265d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3684d3e23556543353655e359c493bf47474c602","tid":1426401,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"080f1b97d810ec64f76ebdc75673e431d9bc4183","tid":1426401,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:11:07.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"04a2b5b4d62fefc9058e9f1bda0f1a226f4bc85c","tid":1426401,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"144cd69605dcd8c0f679f91f756419a9f93ebcfc","tid":1426401,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited